node.title: Body of missing fisherman found in sea near Raglan
node.description: A body recovered from the sea near Raglan has been identified as one of two fishermen who went missing three weeks ago.
node.content:
["A body recovered from the sea near Raglan has been identified as one of two fishermen who went missing three weeks ago.", "", "
\nPhoto: Supplied / Derek Morrison\n
", "He's been identified as Olson Canatoy, aged 52.", "Canatoy's body was recovered at Papanui Point on Sunday.", "His fishing companion, Eric Dabalos, is still missing."]
